data.description: This amazing split level is completely updated inside and out. New, New, New, Everything! New kitchen with stainless appliances, granite countertops and tile backsplash. Two brand new, full bathrooms, new AC and furnace, water heater, new deck & windows, new siding, roof, driveway, lighting and landscaping. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home checks all of the boxes! Situated on a beautiful one acre lot on a tree lined cul de sac, you'll enjoy lots of privacy and potential. Full of natural light with an open, welcoming feel, you'll enjoy being home on the cool fall nights. Look forward to next spring and a fully fenced backyard perfect for a huge garden, pets, kids, yard games, family, friends or relaxing. Welcome Home!
